I"āO<h1 id="introduction">Introduction</h1>

<p>Unleash the power of Apache Spark for efficient data manipulation! This PySpark cheatsheet equips you with the essential techniques to conquer data wrangling challenges. From filtering and imputing missing values to exploring and transforming your data, this guide provides a concise roadmap to success.
	- Streamline Data Acquisition: Effortlessly read data from various file formats like CSV, JSON, and TXT.
	- Seamless Conversion: Convert pandas DataFrames to PySpark DataFrames for smooth integration within the Spark ecosystem (great for users already familiar with pandas!).
	- In-Depth Exploration: Gain valuable insights with functionalities to display schema, shape, columns, and distinct values.
	- Precise Filtering: Filter rows and columns based on specific conditions to focus on relevant data subsets.
	- Effective Imputation: Tackle missing values with techniques like filling with constant values.
	- Effortless Transformations: Rename columns, create new columns, and perform typecasting for optimal data preparation.
	- Temporary View Creation: Simplify data querying by creating temporary views from your DataFrames.
	- Clean Session Management: Learn to effectively stop and manage your Spark sessions.</p>

